  "framing": "FCI-Risk is a *heuristic precursor* to the Year-1 margin-matching theorem. Unlike the P0 V4 formula which collapsed to R\u0302*_iso (P14), FCI-Risk pushes an affine correction inside the non-linear min() and therefore cannot be algebraically reduced to isotonic. Theoretical lineage: Patrini et al. 2017 forward-correction, Liu & Tao 2015 anchor points. Year-1 must derive the M^{-1/3} boundary rate and finite-sample bias bound that this estimator family satisfies under BT; this script only checks empirical feasibility."
